IOTA Reader from Lit.ge offers an incredible reading experience for Lit.ge Books, Magazines and Newspapers on your iPad, iPhone and iPod.  Lit.ge is the first Georgian shop for eBooks offering hundreds of Georgian books. It also offers some foreign books but primarily is oriented on Georgian language reader. Using this application it is very easy to search for, buy and read a desired book on Lit.ge. 

IOTA Reader has the following features:
 • Free Georgian eBooks;
• Turn pages with the flick of a finger;
• Auto synchronize your device with personal library on Lit.ge; 
• Adjustable font size - make the text as big as you want for comfortable reading; 
• Multiple font types;
• Embedded Georgian fonts so you can read in the typeface you like best, without installing Georgian Fonts on your device;
 • Brightness control for easy reading in any light; 
• Night reading mode;
• The ability to search inside the book and look up terms; 
• Add bookmarks;
 • Use Georgian text to speech to read the books;
• And many more…
